These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: scientific, superhero, comedy, satire, fantasy
There are 5 different nationalities: brazilian, british, chinese, pakistani, russian
There are 5 different favourite colors: red, black, aquamarine, apricot, blood-red
5 different games are played: snooker, chess, billiard, bridge, poker
 1. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 2. the person playing poker is the person watching fantasy movies##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the right of the brazilian##1
 4. the person playing snooker is on the right of the chinese##1
 5. the person who likes black is the pakistani##1
 6. the british is the person watching superhero movies##1
 7. the person who likes red is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 8. the british is on the far left##1
 9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the british##1
10. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
11. the person who likes black is the person playing snooker##1
12. the person who likes aquamarine is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Movie-Genre         | superhero  | scientific    | satire | comedy    | fantasy  |
| Nationality   | british  | brazilian | chinese | pakistani | russian  |
| Color           | red     | blood-red     | apricot  | black   | aquamarine    |
| Game         | billiard | bridge    | chess | snooker  | poker |

