.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: skydiving, drawing, camping, filmmaking, puzzles
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daisy, begonia, azalea, rose, tulip
5 different games are played: go, billiard, snooker, backgammon, domino
There are 5 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, mexican, russian, spanish
 1. the person who growsrose is on the right of the argentine##1
 2. the mexican is the person playing billiard##1
 3. the indonesian is on the right of the russian##1
 4. the person playing snooker is on the far left##1
 5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 7. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person playing go##1
 8. the person who's hobby is camping is the person playing snooker##1
 9. the russian is the person who's hobby is camping##1
10. the person who's hobby is drawing is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the mexican##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who growsbegonia##1
13. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Hobby          | camping        | puzzles | drawing     | filmmaking      | skydiving  |
| Flower           | begonia   | azalea | tulip    | rose | daisy |
| Game   | snooker | backgammon     | domino | go    | billiard  |
| Nationality   | russian     | indonesian | argentine    | spanish      | mexican    |

