.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, milk, sprite, tea, water
City: paris, liverpool, nizza, boston, marseilles
The people have 5 different jobs:  manager, musician, police-officer, social-worker, scientist
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, kiwi, banana, watermelon, avocado
 1. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the scientist##1
 2. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 3. the manager is in the middle##1
 4. the person drinking milk is in the middle##1
 5. the police-officer is on the far right##1
 6. the person traveling to liverpool is on the far left##1
 7. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person eating kiwi##1
 8. the police-officer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 9. the person eating avocado is in the middle##1
10. the person eating banana is on the right of the musician##1
11. the police-officer is the person traveling to paris##1
12. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
13. the person drinking tea is the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Beverage      | tea          | sprite  | milk       | fanta     | water      |
| City         | liverpool | marseilles | boston  | nizza   | paris    |
| Job   | musician        | scientist | manager | social-worker    | police-officer   |
| Food     | asparagus   | banana | avocado      | kiwi | watermelon |

