 3. the engineer is the person watching horror movies##1
 4. the paramedic is the person watching drama movies##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the doctor##1
 6. the argentine is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 7. the nigerian is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 8. the french is in the middle##1
 9. the doctor is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
10. the person who's sport is tennis is the designer##1
11. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
12. the spanish is on the left of the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Sport          | basketball        | baseball       | volleyball | sailing   | tennis  |
