 3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the far left##1
 4. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
 5. the person playing billiard is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 9. the person traveling to venice is the person who's sport is cricket##1
10. the person traveling to miami is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
13. the person playing backgammon is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
14. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3    |       4       |    5     |
