.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, oliveros, baccarat, prince, vegafina
There are 5 different favourite colors: grey, green, mauve, brown, turquise
The people have 5 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks, video-games, drawing, fishing
5 different pets are kept: ferret, hedgehog, mouse, pony, rabbit
 1. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1
 3. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 5. the person who likes grey is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 6. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the person who likes green is the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 9. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the prince-smoker##1
10. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
11. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
12. the person who likes mauve is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
13. the person who likes turquise is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Cigar      | bluemaster      | oliveros       | vegafina         | prince  | baccarat |
| Color   | mauve  | brown | green | grey  | turquise  |
| Hobby   | drawing    | magic-tricks    | writing        | fishing | video-games     |
| Pet           | hedgehog | mouse      | ferret       | pony   | rabbit   |

