 1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
 3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the vegafina-smoker##1
 4. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 6. the aristoff-smoker is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is the havana-smoker##1
 8. the person watching sports movies is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person driving the subway is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
11. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
12. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
13. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

