5 different games are played: bridge, monopoly, poker, canasta, scrabble
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: animation, mystery, disaster, family, comedy
 1. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing canasta##1
 2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the fan of trance is the person watching animation movies##1
 4. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is the person who growsbegonia##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 7. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the fan of indie##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is in the middle##1
10. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person playing poker##1
11. the fan of blues is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
12. the fan of rock is the person who growsbellflower##1
13. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1

