City: marseilles, colone, nizza, london, boston
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of punk is the person traveling to marseilles##1
 3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the fan of punk##1
 4. the fan of blues is the cape-cod house##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
 6. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
 7. the fan of pop is the townhouse house##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 9. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person who's sport is rowing is on the far left##1
11. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
12. the fan of salsa is in the middle##1
13. the farmhouse house is the person who's sport is cycling##1
14. the cottage house is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
